<msbt attribsize="4">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，晚安！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今晚的星空非常美麗呢！</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />晚安，<tag a="110" b="1" />。<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />您看過夜空了嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有好多流星喔！
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我們一起來看<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這場美好的星星表演吧！</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了對了！<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我又在書裡發現跟星星有關的方程式，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以把它記下來了！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這個給您，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有空就試做看看吧！</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那麼，希望我們兩個<delay20 />
都能度過一個美好的夜晚！</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="010_01" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />使用<colour id="1" />操控搖桿<colour id="65535" />仰望天空時，<delay20 />
如果看見了流星，<delay frames="30" /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
就按<colour id="1" /><delay20 /><colour id="65535" />來許願看看吧？<delay frames="30" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak />在流星消失之前<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />許下願望的話，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可能會有好事發生喔！<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="010_02" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道您有沒有發現，<delay20 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在這個島上看到的流星，<delay8 />
很多都是短時間內接連劃過的！<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以看到一顆流星，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就繼續仰望天空，
等待下一顆流星<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />出現吧！</message>
	<message label="010_03" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="1" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />您知道每個星座<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都有自己的故事嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果您給我看一些跟星座有關的物品，<delay20 />
我也許可以給您講一些<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我所知道的<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />星座故事喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay frames="30" /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為我是理科生，<delay20 />
很多不可思議的情節，我也不太理解，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以沒有信心能把故事說好<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="011" attrib="02 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay8 />怎麼了嗎？</message>
	<message label="011_a" attrib="00 00 00 00">你看看這個！</message>
	<message label="011_b" attrib="00 00 00 00">來聊天吧</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這是<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />，<delay8 />
對吧！</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那麼，希望我們兩個<delay20 />
都能度過一個美好的夜晚！</message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了對了！<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />之前有一天晚上，<delay8 />
星星比平時閃耀得更美麗，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然後第二天早上我就撿到了這個。
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為實在太漂亮了，<delay20 />
所以我想要分一些<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />給<tag a="110" b="1" />！</message>
	<message label="051" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />關於山羊（魔羯）座的故事<delay8 />有很多種說法，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其中一種是這樣的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak />有一天，眾神在尼羅河畔飲酒聚會時，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />突然出現了一隻叫做狄翁的怪物。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />眾神驚慌失措，<delay8 />紛紛變成動物逃離，<delay20 />
而牧羊神潘恩也化身為山羊跳進尼羅河裡躲藏，<delay20 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但在驚慌之下，僅將下半身變成了魚。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />天神宙斯見狀，覺得有趣，<delay8 />
便將半羊半魚的樣子化成為星座，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />並取名為山羊座。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是一個令人匪夷所思的故事呢，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />竟然把一個變身失敗的樣子化成為星座，<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />潘恩<delay8 />也是滿可憐的呢<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="052" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />關於水瓶座的故事<delay8 />有很多種說法，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其中一種是這樣的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />從前從前，在奧林匹斯神殿中，<delay20 />
有一位叫做黑貝的少女，<delay8 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />負責為眾神倒酒，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但因為要結婚了，<delay20 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />便尋找下一個能負責倒酒的人。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />於是黑貝的父親宙斯<delay8 />便化身為老鷹，<delay8 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />將一位叫做加里美底的俊俏少年，<delay20 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />強行抓來接任倒酒的工作！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak />由於替眾神倒酒是一項很光榮的工作，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了讓加里美底的父母也能看見兒子的樣子，<delay20 />
於是就把他拿著水瓶的樣子化成為星座。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是一個令人匪夷所思的故事呢，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />竟然突然被抓住，<delay8 />還被強行帶走，<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣帥哥也太可憐了吧<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="053" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />關於雙魚座的故事<delay8 />有很多種說法，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其中一種是這樣的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak />有一天，眾神在尼羅河畔飲酒聚會時，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />突然出現了一隻叫做狄翁的怪物。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />眾神驚慌失措，<delay8 />紛紛跳進尼羅河中逃離，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />艾弗黛特為了防止和兒子耶羅斯走散，<delay8 />
便將兩人用繩子綁在一起。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />隨後，兩人就化身為魚形逃走。<delay20 />
據說雙魚座就是<delay8 />
這兩條魚用繩子綁在一起的樣子。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是令人匪夷所思的故事呢，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />艾弗黛特是愛與美的女神，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要化成星座的話，用她原來的樣子比較好吧。</message>
	<message label="054" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />關於牡羊座的故事<delay8 />有很多種說法，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其中一種是這樣的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在某個國家，國王和皇后生下了一對<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />叫做波里庫斯塞斯和黑蕾<delay8 />
的雙胞胎兄妹。<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是，國王卻和皇后離婚了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />新皇后總是欺負這對兄妹，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />把兩人視作眼中釘。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最後，新皇后的陰謀得逞，<delay20 />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就在兄妹二人<delay8 />命在旦夕之際，<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />原本的皇后<delay8 />向天神宙斯求助，<delay20 />
派出黃金羊從天而降<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />將兄妹二人救出，<delay8 />帶向高高的天空。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />於是這隻黃金羊便化成為牡羊座。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是令人匪夷所思的故事呢，<delay20 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為什麼<delay8 />天神宙斯<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總是出現在星座故事裡啊。</message>
	<message label="055" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />關於金牛座的故事<delay8 />有很多種說法，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其中一種是這樣的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />從前從前，<delay8 />某個地方，<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有一位叫做歐羅巴的美麗公主。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有一天，當歐羅巴公主和家臣們<delay8 />
一起在海邊的牧場遊玩時，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知從何處冒出了一隻白色的牛。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這隻牛溫馴又容易親近，<delay8 />
當歐羅巴騎上牛背的時候，<delay20 /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
那隻牛卻突然越過海面飛奔了起來。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />原來那隻牛是天神宙斯變的，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為想要娶美麗的歐羅巴公主，<delay20 />
才強行把她帶走。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />金牛座就是那隻牛的樣子化成的，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而歐羅巴公主被帶去的那片大陸，<delay8 />
後來也被稱之為「歐洲大陸」。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是令人匪夷所思的故事呢，<delay20 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />天神宙斯這樣做<delay frames="30" /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
不會有點太過分嗎<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="056" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />關於雙子座的故事<delay8 />有很多種說法，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其中一種是這樣的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />從前從前，<delay8 />在天神宙斯的兒子當中，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有一對<delay8 />名為卡斯托魯<delay8 />和
普魯克斯的攣生兄弟。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />他們兄弟二人感情深厚且驍勇善戰，<delay8 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但唯獨只有普魯克斯<delay20 />
繼承了宙斯的血脈，擁有不死之身。<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在一次戰役中，<delay8 />卡斯托魯不幸身亡，<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />傷心欲絕的普魯克斯決定放棄不死之身，<delay20 />
跟隨卡斯托魯一起升上夜空，成為雙子座。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是令人匪夷所思的故事呢，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />他們的兄弟之情<delay8 />確實很令人感動，<10_4 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但無法想像他們是宙斯的兒子<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="057" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />關於巨蟹座的故事<delay8 />有很多種說法，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其中一種是這樣的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />從前從前，<delay8 />有一隻叫做西多拉的怪物，
在泉水裡下了毒，讓人民十分困擾，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />海克力斯知道了，便前去趕走西多拉。<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />經過一番苦戰後，<delay8 />正當海克力斯要
給西多拉致命一擊時，<delay frames="30" /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一隻巨大的螃蟹
前來幫助西多拉，<delay20 />但卻被無情地踩死了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />宙斯的妻子希拉覺得這隻螃蟹很可憐，<delay8 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />於是將牠化成為星座，也就是現在的巨蟹座。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是令人匪夷所思的故事呢，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過在危急時刻有朋友趕來相助，真不錯。<10_4 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />即使那是一隻可怕的怪獸朋友<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="058" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />關於獅子座的故事<delay8 />有很多種說法，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其中一種是這樣的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽說在希臘的尼米亞森林中，<delay8 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />住著一隻會吃人的獅子。<delay20 />
海克力斯決定要去趕走那隻獅子。<pageBreak />無論是弓箭、棍棒還是劍都傷害不了那隻獅子，
最後海克力斯徒手掐住獅子的脖子<delay8 />
整整三天三夜，<delay8 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />才將獅子擊敗。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />天神宙斯的妻子希拉認為<delay20 />
與海克力斯大戰的<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那隻獅子相當勇猛，
為了頌揚牠，<delay20 />便將牠化成為星座。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是令人匪夷所思的故事呢，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />究竟海力克斯<delay8 />和希拉之間<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有著怎樣的過節呢<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="059" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />關於處女座的故事<delay8 />有很多種說法，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其中一種是這樣的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />宙斯和迪米特有一個女兒，<delay8 />叫做波塞弗尼。<delay20 />
有一天波塞弗尼外出採花，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />卻不幸被冥界之王普魯托擄走。<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />農業女神迪米特知道之後，<delay20 />
因為悲傷過度，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />害得地上的農作物都無法生長。<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />宙斯不忍心再看到百姓們痛苦，<delay8 />
便去說服了普魯托，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓母女倆最後得以重逢。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而拿著稻穗的處女座，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />據說就是母親迪米特的樣子。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是令人匪夷所思的故事呢，<delay20 />
<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />竟然是用母親的形象而不是女兒。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且，<delay frames="30" /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />怎麼說那都是宙斯自己的女兒，
怎麼不早點行動呢<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="060" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />關於天秤座的故事<delay8 />有很多種說法，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其中一種是這樣的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />正義女神阿斯托蕾雅<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有一架能測量人類善惡的神秘天秤，<delay8 />
還可以將惡人打入冥界。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />據說在潘朵拉打開那個<delay8 />
封住世界災難的盒子之前，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這架天秤幾乎毫無用處。<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而這架神祕的天秤，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />據說就是天秤座的原型。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是一個匪夷所思的故事呢，<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />人的善惡竟然可以用重量來秤<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="061" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />關於天蠍座的故事<delay8 />有很多種說法，<delay frames="40" />
